and the wild beast of Revelation 17 verse 16

00:09:47.480 --> 00:09:49.480
turn on Babylon the Great,

00:09:49.480 --> 00:09:52.480
the world empire of false religion.

00:09:52.480 --> 00:09:54.480
Let us bear in mind

00:09:54.480 --> 00:09:57.480
that God will put it into their hearts

00:09:57.480 --> 00:09:59.480
to make that move,

00:09:59.480 --> 00:10:02.480
and this could happen swiftly,

00:10:02.480 --> 00:10:04.480
and at any time,

00:10:04.480 --> 00:10:07.480
the end of this entire system of things

00:10:07.480 --> 00:10:11.730
is not far off.

00:10:11.730 --> 00:10:13.730
Brothers and sisters,

00:10:13.730 --> 00:10:17.730
do you sense the urgency in those words?

00:10:17.730 --> 00:10:20.730
It may be that until now,

00:10:20.730 --> 00:10:22.730
you thought that some world event

00:10:22.730 --> 00:10:24.730
would make it clear

00:10:24.730 --> 00:10:27.730
that you need to return to Jehovah,

00:10:27.730 --> 00:10:29.730
but the Bible tells us

00:10:29.730 --> 00:10:31.730
that the Great Tribulation

00:10:31.730 --> 00:10:34.730
will break out with such suddenness

00:10:34.730 --> 00:10:37.730
that it will catch people unaware,

00:10:37.730 --> 00:10:40.730
leaving no time to make changes.

00:10:40.730 --> 00:10:42.730
Really then,

00:10:42.730 --> 00:10:44.730
if you have been inactive

00:10:44.730 --> 00:10:49.730
and waiting for the right time to return,

00:10:49.730 --> 00:10:51.730
this is it,

00:10:51.730 --> 00:10:53.730
and you can be sure

00:10:53.730 --> 00:10:56.730
that Jehovah will welcome you back home.

00:10:56.730 --> 00:10:59.730
He views each sheep

00:10:59.730 --> 00:11:02.730
as a valuable part of his congregation.

00:11:02.730 --> 00:11:04.730
In fact,

00:11:04.730 --> 00:11:07.730
notice what Jehovah says about his people

00:11:07.730 --> 00:11:11.730
at Malachi chapter 3 and verse 17.

00:11:11.730 --> 00:11:15.730
Now, as we read the words in this verse,

00:11:15.730 --> 00:11:17.730
think about the value

00:11:17.730 --> 00:11:19.730
that Jehovah places

00:11:19.730 --> 00:11:22.730
on each individual in his organization,

00:11:22.730 --> 00:11:26.730
including those who may have drifted.

00:11:26.730 --> 00:11:29.730
At Malachi chapter 3 and verse 17,

00:11:29.730 --> 00:11:32.730
Jehovah says about his people.

00:11:32.730 --> 00:11:34.730
They will be mine,

00:11:34.730 --> 00:11:36.730
says Jehovah of Armies,

00:11:36.730 --> 00:11:40.730
in the day when I produce a special property.

00:11:40.730 --> 00:11:43.730
The footnote in the New World translation

00:11:43.730 --> 00:11:45.730
