00:11:45.730 --> 00:11:47.730
for special property

00:11:47.730 --> 00:11:50.730
as treasured possession.

00:11:50.730 --> 00:11:51.730
Imagine,

00:11:51.730 --> 00:11:53.730
in Jehovah's eyes,

00:11:53.730 --> 00:11:55.730
even if you have drifted from the flock,

00:11:55.730 --> 00:11:58.730
you have not been discarded.

00:11:58.730 --> 00:12:00.730
And why?

00:12:00.730 --> 00:12:04.730
Because you are still precious to Jehovah.

00:12:04.730 --> 00:12:07.730
They are mine, he says,

00:12:07.730 --> 00:12:10.730
and he views you as special property,

00:12:10.730 --> 00:12:13.730
as a treasured possession.

00:12:13.730 --> 00:12:15.730
That means,

00:12:15.730 --> 00:12:16.730
if you're lost,

00:12:16.730 --> 00:12:19.730
Jehovah wants you to be found.

00:12:19.730 --> 00:12:21.730
If you're hurt,

00:12:21.730 --> 00:12:23.730
he wants you to be healed.

00:12:23.730 --> 00:12:25.730
And we do too.

00:12:25.730 --> 00:12:26.730
After all,

00:12:26.730 --> 00:12:29.730
you are our fathers and mothers,

00:12:29.730 --> 00:12:31.730
sons and daughters,

00:12:31.730 --> 00:12:34.730
brothers and sisters.

00:12:34.730 --> 00:12:36.730
We long for the day

00:12:36.730 --> 00:12:38.730
that you will be reunited with us

00:12:38.730 --> 00:12:43.730
